There is no registration requirement for Data Controllers or data processing activities except that Data Controllers have the obligation to keep records of:&nbsp;

its activities of collection, processing and use of Personal Data; and
its response to damages occurred to Personal Data.&nbsp;

Data Controllers are required to submit records of their response to damages occurred to Personal Data to the National Human Rights Commission annually or at any time as requested by the National Human Rights Commission.Last modified 23 Feb 2022
				
			